Subject: [PATCH 1/4] Revert "settime: Replace int with ssize_t"

This reverts commit 97682a793abaec7e05ea99a9b59a901319562a30.

One hunk of the "time: notify processes when time of day is changed"
is missing. And "settime: Replace int with ssize_t" modifies the
same area. So revert these two commits first and then reapply the
two complete ones.

Signed-off-by: He Zhe <zhe.he@windriver.com>
